{"tid":2024791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【黃色媒體圈】不如做好最壞準備，啟動一個不靠大氣電波壟斷的TVHK","createTime":"2020-05-20T00:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T15:12:26.000Z","uid":138409,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"418651c52983bcb1d044057bb8546544a2784602","tid":2024791,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T00:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o7jyfCm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo7jyfCm.jpg&h=c2ff72f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得武漢肺炎嘅民間資訊網站？<br />\n<a href=\"https://wars.vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwars.vote4.hk%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=38209fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wars.vote4.hk/</a><br />\n仲有區議會投票指南？<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e36c59aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n開發團隊再次歸來<br />\n今次搞嘅係open source電視平台 -- <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TVHK</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n價格更低：採用BitTorrent點對點 (P2P) 技術，省卻數據寄存費用<br />\n廣及全民：電視平台聯盟制度，讓香港人享受無審查的資訊及視聽娛樂<br />\n增加收入：創作者及商店可透過廣告賺取收入<br />\n廣告機遇：推廣產品及服務可遍及各行各業，機遇更大<br />\n接觸面廣：區議會可利用平台，向選區展示工作成績<br />\n支持運動：社會運動人士可透過平台宣傳活動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3202491939763056&amp;set=a.184700218208925&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D3202491939763056%26set%3Da.184700218208925%26type%3D3%26theater&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=cae8e74e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3202491939763056&amp;set=a.184700218208925&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n政府又打壓RTHK。無限期停製《頭條新聞》。甚至將已製作節目下架。香港人的言論自由再受重擊。當我們說，要Liberate HK，我們可能連家中的TV Screen都Liberate不了。<br />\n既然RTHK就死，不如做好最壞準備，啟動一個不靠大氣電波壟斷的TVHK? (唔係王維基果個！）<br />\ntvhk是一個透過軟件 + 硬件製作及播放店內 + 手機 + 網上電視節目的平台，分為兩部分：<br />\n一個類似YouTube的影片網站（電腦及手機版）<br />\n電視機頂盒（創作者及社區版）<br />\n軟件：使用開源（open source）軟件<br />\n硬件：使用時興的自製迷你電腦，以及能容易買到、已下載定製軟件的Android TV Box<br />\ntvhk會⋯⋯<br />\n創造一個交叉銷售網絡的聯盟<br />\n與YouTube共存並用，相得益彰<br />\n讓其他「黃色平台」在此整合宣傳工作，推廣生意更輕鬆<br />\n詳細介紹︰<br />\nEnglish<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1LeB3iHb3LGC9XDpFTKn8jVAOFp6T2R_aQLZyv-y-s7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fpresentation%2Fd%2F1LeB3iHb3LGC9XDpFTKn8jVAOFp6T2R_aQLZyv-y-s7k&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=ff2fd1a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1LeB3iHb3LGC9XDpFTKn8jVAOFp6T2R_aQLZyv-y-s7k</a><br />\n( <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/tvhk/objective/5238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2Ftvhk%2Fobjective%2F5238&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=48dbd6e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/tvhk/objective/5238</a> )<br />\n中文<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1aKgNQlKJFoTk-jmc9P9yYib_OGjErMiZQUlkr1U97Jw/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fpresentation%2Fd%2F1aKgNQlKJFoTk-jmc9P9yYib_OGjErMiZQUlkr1U97Jw%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7qix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=956364f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1aKgNQlKJFoTk-jmc9P9yYib_OGjErMiZQUlkr1U97Jw/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"6d863a6852795dba798ce1ad1e21f3818e3fe5f5","tid":2024791,"uid":107571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T00:10:46.000Z","msg":"唔係好明但推左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b16f157a2b12eba2f7a4456d61f8d815c8a004","tid":2024791,"uid":5094,"like":